data.description: This stunning 4-bed/2.5-bath home is located in the desirable Crosswater community, featuring a vaulted front & dining room area, open kitchen w/newer black ss appliances & cozy living room. Dual-sided gas fireplace. Upstairs bedrooms are spacious & offer plenty of closet space. Large primary features a generous walk-in closet & private ensuite bath w/double sinks, soaking tub & shower. Updated paint throughout & 2021 LVP & carpet upstairs gives this home a fresh, modern feel. Beautiful sunset views of the large NGPA from your covered front porch. Easily maintained large patio & turfed side yard is fenced for privacy. Located in the highly sought-after Lake Stevens SD & minutes away from great schools, parks, the lake, shopping & dining.
